{"tid":445521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"奶西係一門藝術","createTime":"2017-10-23T12:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T15:24:44.000Z","uid":26018,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"153b57e3a23428f7d26eb310420e6ba474465110","tid":445521,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"首先，你要由大腿內側開始奶起，但又唔好咁快就去奶個西，又外至內慢慢黎，等條女個心撈撈亂，撈撈亂，條女會諗到底幾時先黎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢咁build up個氣氛，當然隻手唔可以偷懶，揸波，揸蘿，同埋r乳頭當然唔少得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後由外陰唇慢慢咁奶，好似食生蠔咁，你會feel到有少少咸咸地既味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能一開始會有少少難入口，但就好似第一次食海膽咁，試左就不能自拔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢由外陰唇奶到去內陰唇，條女個西靚就應該唔會好大塊，好好入口，有啲女塊西既內陰唇就大啲，似帶子邊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然唔可以放過啦！講左咁耐都未到重點，就係條女既陰蹄，唔計g點，係最敏感既部份，可以選擇打圈，壓力或者吸吮去品嚐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個時候其實都係條女最high既時間，利用你既中指同無名指慢慢插入條女個西到大概2-3啲，向上彎起，給予適當既節奏，比壓力去撳個西！！當然一定要繼續奶粒陰蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72419bbfa0d6bfbd81d3b3997053848bafcb6bff","tid":445521,"uid":8253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"